short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces all f's with pf's and all instances of the word "millennial" with "Matt Young."

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This app provides the missing support that Pforzheimer House residents need in their Chrome experience. Have you ever read an article and wanted the f's to be replaced by their true form, pf? Have you ever wanted the word millennial replaced with its archetype, Matt Young? Have you ever wanted Google to load improperly in order to meet the above requirements? Then iPfoho is for you!
